│ (CB->isStrictFP() != OtherCB->isStrictFP())\n                │
│ return false;\n"                                             │
│     ]                                                        │
│   ]                                                          │
│ }                                                            │
│ </tool_code>                                                 │
│ ### 5. Conclusion                                            │
│                                                              │
│ By enhancing the equality check in                           │
│ `SimpleValue::isIdenticalTo` to account for the `strictfp`   │
│ attribute, we ensure that `early-cse` does not attempt to    │
│ merge incompatible call sites. This resolves the assertion   │
│ failure and makes the pass more robust by correctly handling │
│ this aspect of call site semantics. The proposed edit is a   │
│ minimal, targeted fix that directly addresses the root cause │
│ of the problem.                                              │
